```mermaid
graph TD
    CLK[clk] --> FSM[[State Register]]
    RST[rst] --> FSM
    NICKEL[nickel] --> FSM
    DIME[dime] --> FSM
    
    FSM --> DECODE(State Decoder)
    DECODE --> DISP[dispense]
    DECODE --> CHG[change[1:0]]
    
    TB[Testbench] -.-> CLK
    TB -.-> RST
    TB -.-> NICKEL
    TB -.-> DIME
    TB -.-> |verify|DISP
    TB -.-> |verify|CHG
    
    subgraph States
        S0[0¢]
        S5[5¢]
        S10[10¢]
        S15[15¢ - Dispense]
    end
    
    S0 -->|nickel| S5
    S0 -->|dime| S10
    S5 -->|nickel| S10
    S5 -->|dime| S15
    S10 -->|nickel| S15
    S10 -->|dime| S15
    S15 --> S0
